{"tid":96282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普威脅：墨西哥不出錢蓋牆　貿易免談","createTime":"2017-01-26T17:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T16:35:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"778046e4c47eb92e4f332f4ee17fc55596345d54","tid":96282,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>川普威脅：墨西哥不出錢蓋牆　貿易免談</strong><br />\n2017年01月26日22:14<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170126/640_33dd0df991517a95b6cd0f42eaa9160d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170126%2F640_33dd0df991517a95b6cd0f42eaa9160d.jpg&h=e315f1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝網路<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普（Donald Trump）昨天正式簽署行政命令，要在美墨邊境蓋起「美墨長城」，杜絕非法移民入境美國。對此，墨西哥總統班尼耶多（Enrique Pena Nieto）再次強調「不會付錢」。<br />\n<br />\n不過川普顯然來硬的，剛剛又在推特發文稱：「<strong>美國與墨西哥有高達600億美元的貿易赤字。</strong>這根本是《北美自由貿易協定》（NAFTA）一開始就一面倒的交易，導致損失大量的工作和企業。如果墨西哥不願意付錢蓋這個迫切需要的牆，我們最好取消接下來的談判」。<span style=\"color: red;\">墨西哥不斷釋出善意，表示願意跟美國重談NAFTA。</span>川普此言是否會引發實質的後續效應，有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n（韓政燕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170126/1044718/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170126%2F1044718%2F&d=CkZeMYszKo0ts%2FLqs7T89XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ced1b17a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170126/1044718/</a>"},{"pid":"78a3207a8dba75187d1838e505f4d4acde109ffd","tid":96282,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"推 a29976137: 300億城牆換600億貿易 <br />\n<br />\n推 kiergh: 搞到墨西哥爆走 對美國沒比較好吧 <br />\n<br />\n推 Crazyfire: 墨西哥當然是不可能付錢 但把NAFTA給取消掉 墨西哥對美 <br />\n&rarr; Crazyfire: 的大量順差縮減的話 也算是被川普間接逼到付錢啦 <br />\n<br />\n&rarr; Crazyfire: 圍牆一定蓋得起來早就可以預見的 但沒NAFTA的北美經濟 <br />\n&rarr; Crazyfire: 會如何 就真的無法預測了...... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推 flyop: 墨西哥應該也提供不少便宜人力吧？ <br />\n<br />\n&rarr; lookatme921: 叫你付就付<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推 Crazyfire: 美墨圍牆的成本大概100億鎂 但只要墨西哥對美順差減少 <br />\n&rarr; Crazyfire: 一半 約300億鎂 就等於足以&quot;付錢&quot;給美國蓋三座了 <br />\n<br />\n推 barry1027gg: 叫墨西哥人出錢蓋長城再阻止墨西哥人 狂! <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1485440378.A.D80.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1485440378.A.D80.html&d=CkZeMYszKo0ts%2FLqs7T89XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a1035e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1485440378.A.D80.html</a>"},{"pid":"32117ff018f4896412a7699858b6d45708a2e8cc","tid":96282,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"侵侵真係好勁 <br />\n佢e招已經唔係第一次用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢本書寫過佢曾經買一幅地 州政府獅子開大口加佢價 <br />\n點知佢還價 減一半 再還價減一半 再還價減一半 <br />\n最後迫到政府賣比佢 十幾年後 因為起機場導致嘈音問題 <br />\n政府最後要賠凸比佢"},{"pid":"96e00346f2a827e07f766acdfdd3bedda6f49a45","tid":96282,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0697c98ca33267dc6ea68c464478191804484c","tid":96282,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:21:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵侵真係好勁 <br />\n佢e招已經唔係第一次用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢本書寫過佢曾經買一幅地 州政府獅子開大口加佢價 <br />\n點知佢還價 減一半 再還價減一半 再還價減一半 <br />\n最後迫到政府賣比佢 十幾年後 因為起機場導致嘈音問題 <br />\n政府最後要賠凸比佢</blockquote><br />\n點樣令佢減一半又可以迫到賣比佢，可唔可以講多d"},{"pid":"d84a81e04a5cd292406f9497e69bc97b5b1627e7","tid":96282,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"玩到NAFTA真係同迫墨西哥比錢冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla